  <h1>Privacy Policy – Cart Keeper</h1>

  <p>Cart Keeper ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our smart shopping, pantry, and to-do app.</p>

  <strong>1. Information We Collect</strong>
  <p><b>Account Data:</b> When you sign up or log in, we collect your email address and password. This information is securely stored in our database.</p>
  <p><b>List Data:</b> Your shopping lists, pantry items, and to-dos are stored on our servers to support syncing across devices.</p>
  <p><b>Usage Data:</b> We collect technical data like device type, OS, and basic in-app activity to help improve performance.</p>

  <strong>2. How We Use Your Data</strong>
  <p>We use your information to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Authenticate your account</li>
    <li>Sync your lists and items securely between devices</li>
    <li>Provide smart recommendations and features</li>
    <li>Improve app stability and performance</li>
  </ul>

  <strong>3. Data Storage and Sync</strong>
  <p>Your data is stored securely in our database and is only accessible to you. We do not share or sell this information to third parties.</p>

  <strong>4. Security</strong>
  <p>Passwords are hashed before storage. All communications with our API are encrypted using HTTPS. While we apply best practices, no system is 100% secure.</p>

  <strong>5. Your Rights</strong>
  <p>You can:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>View and edit your data within the app</li>
    <li>Delete your lists or your entire account</li>
    <li>Request full data removal by contacting us</li>
  </ul>

  <strong>6. Children’s Privacy</strong>
  <p>Our app is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children. Please contact us if you believe we have.</p>

  <strong>7. Policy Updates</strong>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected in the app and on this page.</p>

  <p><strong>Contact:</strong> feldman.ofer11@gmail.com<br>
  <strong>Last updated:</strong> July 17, 2025</p>
</body>
